Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:23:01.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}衝動 切望 Starting over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:06.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}生まれ変わるなら 怖れないで
